sections.heading: to 10-12A-13 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1992, ch. 118, § 20 repealed 10-12A-1 to 10-12A-13 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1984, ch. 119, §§ 1 to 13, relating to magistrate retirement, effective July 1, 1992. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1991 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.For present comparable provisions,see10-12C-1 NMSA 1978 et seq.
